{"entity_timestamp": "2026-03-29T06:25:18+00:00", "entity_id": "baf3f635-1091-560e-bbca-eac34c885be0", "alert": {"header_text": "Planned work: Mordialloc Station changes from August", "description_text": "9pm Monday 18 August From August, we’ll implement the following changes to enable Mordialloc level crossing removal works:  From 9pm Monday 18 August, the underpass will close. To access Platform 1, please detour via McDonald Street, Bear Street and Main Street. From Friday 29 August until mid 2026, Platform 2 will close. All train services will depart from Platform 1. Frankston Line trains will run to an altered timetable from Friday 29 August until mid 2026. The majority of the station car park remains closed. Pedestrian access may be subject to change.  Find out more about how we’re keeping the Frankston Line moving during these works.", "severity_level": null, "cause": "OTHER_CAUSE", "effect": "OTHER_EFFECT", "informed_entities": [{"agency_id": "1", "route_id": "aus:vic:vic-02-FKN:", "direction_id": 1, "stop_id": "vic:rail:MOR"}, {"agency_id": "1", "route_id": "aus:vic:vic-02-FKN:", "direction_id": 0, "stop_id": "vic:rail:MOR"}, {"agency_id": "1", "route_id": "aus:vic:vic-02-FKN-R:", "direction_id": 1, "stop_id": "vic:rail:MOR"}, {"agency_id": "1", "route_id": "aus:vic:vic-02-FKN-R:", "direction_id": 0, "stop_id": "vic:rail:MOR"}], "active_periods": [{"start": "2025-08-18T11:00:00+00:00", "end": "2026-05-05T13:59:00+00:00"}]}, "ingest_timestamp": "2026-03-29T06:25:56+00:00"}
